summary:
...TAMMY MOVING SLOWLY NORTHWESTWARD WITH LITTLE CHANGE IN STRENGTH...
 As of 5:00 PM AST Fri Oct 27
 the center of Tammy was located near 32.5, -61.4
 with movement NW at 3 mph.
 The minimum central pressure was 988 mb
 with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
